import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
from pandas.io.json import json_normalize

def json_parse(filename):
    data = pd.read_json('data/' + filename)
    data = json_normalize(data['result'])
    return data

filename = 'btc-ltc-daily.json'

data = json_parse(filename)
